name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Black Dodge Red Stripes Live Wallpaper

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Unleash power with the Black Dodge Red Stripes live wallpaper, featuring a clock and Google search bar for your new tab.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Turn your Chrome new tab into a bold statement with the Black Dodge Red Stripes Live Wallpaper. This 4K extension features a stunning Dodge muscle car with striking red racing stripes that exude speed, power, and style. Designed for car enthusiasts and those who love dynamic visuals, this wallpaper captures the essence of modern automotive performance. The minimalist layout includes a built-in clock and Google search bar, ensuring your browsing experience is both functional and stylish. Add a touch of adrenaline and sophistication to your screen with this high-performance live wallpaper.

Extension Features
4K Live Wallpaper:
Ultra-high-definition visuals of the Black Dodge with bold red racing stripes.

Minimalist Layout:
A clean design that keeps your new tab visually appealing and distraction-free.

Integrated Clock:
Stay on time with a sleek, built-in clock displayed on your new tab.

Google Search Bar:
Quick access to Google search for added convenience.

Dynamic and Powerful:
The aggressive design of the Dodge with red stripes adds energy to your browser.

Optimized Performance:
Lightweight and efficient, ensuring smooth operation for an enhanced browsing experience.

Perfect for Auto Enthusiasts:
Celebrate speed and design with every new tab you open.
